<P>
Photo, Sen. Pete Wilson at his desk in Washington office as he returned to 
legislative duties. BERNIE BOSTON / Los Angeles Times; Photo, His opponent, 
Dianne Feinstein, continued to make an issue of his attendance record. JAYNE 
KAMIN-ONCEA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
