<TYPE>
<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
MCDONNEL DOUGLAS CORP; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; AEROSPACE 
INDUSTRY -- LABOR RELATIONS; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- LAYOFFS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
