The Phoenix Cardinals traded injury-prone defensive end David Galloway, who has 
played only 24 regular-season games the last four seasons, to the Denver 
Broncos for an undisclosed draft pick. . . . Cardinal guard Lance Smith was 
arrested in connection with a domestic dispute but is expected to play Sunday 
against the New York Giants. 
