"therapeutic." ; Photo, Los Lobos (from left: David Hidalgo, Steve Berlin, 
Cesar Rosas, Conrad Lozano and Louie Perez) hope their new album expresses 
peace. JOSE GALVEZ / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
