<P>
Photo, Bob Welch Associated Press; Photo, Sliding in safe -- Carney Lansford of 
the Oakland A's advances to third base around the reach of Cincinnati's Chris 
Sabo in the World Series opener Tuesday night. The Reds won, 7-0. (Story, C1) 
United Press International 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
